Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just supposed to be an ordinary third grader,\N but then a small incident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I received was a courageous heart.\N What I gained were magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings have become more powerful, since what\N I've always believed in is resonating so strongly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to stop communicating, because I can't\N stand it when someone is left in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:01:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always so uneasy that I was shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hugging my knees in the corner of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of knowing the "truth"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and closed the door to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through a kind lie, I discovered where I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fled and took refuge in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows of the lonely sea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,being dyed a deep blue color
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that hides my loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With wholehearted feelings, I wounded your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret within your eyes makes me want to soak it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the truth behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your smile with a warm love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I touch it, the warmth that seems so breakable will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,break away from its past and overflow.\NBecause you're always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will no longer be puzzled over the shadow of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been thinking about her since we met...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About that girl who had such deep, beautiful eyes...\N who seemed just about the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure we'll just clash if we ever meet again, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings That Can't Be Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been staring off into space and zoning out since\N the other day, no matter what we talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Alisa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If talking to us really is that boring,\N then just go ahead and zone out by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Suzuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alisa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Suzuka-chan.\N It really was my fault this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's really true... but anyway, Alisa-chan\N went completely overboard just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go have a talk with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I made her angry... I'm sorry, Alisa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alisa-chan... Alisa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alisa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sort of understand why you're so angry,\N but you can't get angry over things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it really annoys me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so obvious that she's worried about something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written all over her face that\N she's lost and troubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... no matter how many times we ask\N her about it, she won't tell us a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's {\i1}lying{\i0} when she says she's not lost or troubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody has something they keep secret,\N even from their closest friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Nanoha-chan wants to keep it a secret,\N don't you think all we can do is wait for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what annoys me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we could help her, at least a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything would be fine, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't do anything about whatever it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the very least, we can all worry about it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do like Nanoha-chan, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she was there for me, I was no longer alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Nanoha-chan was there,\N we were all able to become friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha-chan, we're sorry.\N We both have lessons today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be gone till late tonight, right?\N Have a nice time, and do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alisa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sure everything will turn\N out all right, Nanoha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks, Suzuka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I think about it... it's been a\N while since I've walked home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess I'll make a stop before I go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...because I don't want anyone\N to see my face right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we all first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was a lot weaker than I am now,\N and I could never say what I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone said or did to me,\N I could never stand up to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was a terrible kid who thought only\N of herself... I was selfish, and a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always made fun of our classmates\N and joked about everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because my heart was really weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... that's mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was weak back then too,\N I couldn't say what I wanted to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That it was really precious to me,\N so if you could please give it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after you told me to stop, I didn't listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I thought that if I listened\N to what someone else had to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd lose for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it Nanoha-chan said back then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Does that hurt? The hearts of people who have their\N precious things taken away hurt a whole lot more!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, I got into a big fight\N with Alisa-chan, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the one who stopped us was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incredibly quiet girl who decided to be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then... it was because I was so desperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, we slowly began to talk more\N and more to each other, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... just the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What did you want from me,\N after bringing up that old story?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know the answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that she doesn't want the\N two of us to worry about her, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which also means that we probably\N can't help her do anything about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all we can do is wait, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just stay angry while I'm waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angry at the sadness of not being\N able to understand her feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and at her, for not being able to rely\N on the strength of her best friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so you got into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it. Alisa-chan just got\N mad because I was zoning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of your best friends, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Almost since I first started school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your share.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have cram school today...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I should be able to do some Jewel Seed\N hunting, at least until dinnertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food they have here... isn't all that bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's see what my little princess is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, almost forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't touched your meal again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good... you have to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had some of it... I'm fine, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get going, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been able to get a rough estimate of\N where the next Jewel Seed should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't want to keep Mother waiting for too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... because you're my master, Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and because I'm your familiar...\N if you ask me to go, I'll go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we can go after you finish eating, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not what I meant.\N I'm worried about you, Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using wide area searching magic uses\N up a lot of physical strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet you're hardly eating anything, and barely resting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your wound isn't something\N you can take lightly, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, because I'm strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's go. Mother's waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyouya... about Nanoha-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has she been worried about something recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how she looked when I saw her earlier,\N and Suzuka's pretty worried about her, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... she has been going\N out a lot at night recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be prying a bit too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but do you think maybe you could\N ask her to talk to me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the offer, but...\N I don't really think she'll talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm no good...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's not it! That's definitely not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that she won't talk to you specifically,\N but that she probably won't talk to anyone about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been like that, whenever\N she's been worried about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll be able to solve\N whatever it is on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has so many features, it'll surprise\N you every time! Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I might be out of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to get home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. I'll stay around\N here and search a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... but will you be all right by yourself, Yuuno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Go home and get some dinner, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alisa-chan and Suzuka-chan should be on\N their way home from lessons right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure it's somewhere around here,\N but I can only get a rough reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can understand... searching through\N this much garbage must be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bit heavy-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'll release a lot of magical power across the\N circumference of this area and force it to activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait a second. I'll do that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be all right? You'll be\N pretty drained afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just whose familiar do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A forced activation spell in the city?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really dangerous! Hope I make it in time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raising Heart, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like {\i1}she's{\i0} nearby, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and finish things, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bardiche!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.05,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Form, Set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nanoha, can you see the activated Jewel Seed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. It's really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That other girl's really close, too.\N Seal it before she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyrical Magical!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jewel Seed Serial XIX!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.34,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Device Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I first met both Alisa-chan and\N Suzuka-chan, we weren't friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because we couldn't talk with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because we couldn't understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason Alisa-chan got angry with me this morning\N was because I couldn't tell her what I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Nanoha, hurry up and secure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we'll let her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because we both have the same goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there might be no way we\N can avoid fighting like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, we couldn't properly introduce ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nanoha! Takamachi Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A third grader who attends then\N Seishou Auxiliary Elementary School.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:21.59,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does she have such lonely eyes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.24,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Flier Fin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending an e-mail to Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Telling her we just finished our lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah! Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you solve your problem soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best. We'll always be\N cheering you on. Suzuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:32.47,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Flash Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.25,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.01,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Defencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said nothing would change just by talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm sure there are things we can't communicate\N to each other without using words!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might not be able to do anything about\N competing with each other like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I can't stand fighting like this without\N knowing anything about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, I was gathering the Jewel Seeds because\N Yuuno-kun was searching for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because Yuuno-kun needs to gather and\N return them to where they belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was here to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a coincidence that I ended up helping him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but now I'm gathering the\N Jewel Seeds of my own free will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to put the people\N around me or my city in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... my reason for doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate! You don't have to answer her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:22:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell anything to people who are just\N acting nice to you in a strange neighborhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who are probably just trying to use you anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our top priority is to capture the Jewel Seeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.34,0:22:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuka, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I'm starving. Let's hurry back home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. I was stumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.87,0:23:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and losing my way on my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since you were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the silver wind came looking for\N two who were lacking something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.56,0:24:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond the cellophane sea and forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.26,0:24:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just crying in our city that's\N nothing more than a diorama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.77,0:24:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you held out to me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.54,0:24:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the ever-swaying years,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.23,0:24:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt you looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.91,0:24:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I had finally, finally found the secret key.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. Gather the lemon-colored
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.15,0:24:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drops of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.82,0:24:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to gently light the path you're walking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish, even if it's a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.73,0:24:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you can't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.35,0:24:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then remember that because you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.18,0:25:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.92,0:25:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}An explosion that large...\N this is seriously dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.46,0:25:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}But... Mother's waiting, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.69,0:25:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}The true identity of the\N Jewel Seeds, and a new mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.49,0:25:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Next time on\N Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.70,0:25:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Episode Seven:\N The Third Mage!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.20,0:25:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Lyrical Magical won't lose!
